dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Noah Hill. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Pamela Walker.
Nice to meet you, Pamela. Could you please provide me with your policy number for identification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is zero zero two five.
Thank you, Pamela. Can you also confirm your date of birth for verification?
My date of birth is the twenty-fourth of May, nineteen eighty-seven.
Great, thank you for verifying that information, Pamela. How can I assist you today with Old Stone Auto Insurance?
I would like to inquire about my policy coverage and if I can add a new vehicle to it.
Of course, Pamela. Let's review your current policy coverage first and then discuss adding the new vehicle. How about we schedule a callback to dive deeper into this?
That works for me. Thank you, Noah, for your assistance.
You're welcome, Pamela. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
